lines.line: I used to hide from the world, finding comfort in the shadows beneath my bed.
Then I discovered joy in the simple things, like chasing a colorful ball across the floor.
Now I sit here, eyes wide with wonder, realizing life's greatest adventures happen when we open our hearts.

parsed_script.full_script: I used to hide from the world, finding comfort in the shadows beneath my bed. Then I discovered joy in the simple things, like chasing a colorful ball across the floor. Now I sit here, eyes wide with wonder, realizing life's greatest adventures happen when we open our hearts.
